name: Bunny Commits Carrot Crimes
description:
You are a bunny who is trying to get to a party but you need to bring carrots with you! Make your way through the level and make sure the pesky root vegetables do not stop your progress!

Hold Left Click and Release - Jump

Right click - Rotate axe
